	<dl>
	<dt>Because, A) At 17 years old its been...</dt>
	<dd><p>Because, A) At 17 years old its been decided that I couldn't possibly know enough to have a say in the politics of this country.</p> <p>B) The vote is a useless tool for effecting any change, being given a choice only between a bunch of clones wearing different colour ties.</p>
	<small>
	written 15th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/869">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=869">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

